               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430130-name-932" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430130-name-932" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430130-name-932" type="surname" value="HOLT"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430130-name-932" type="given" value="EDWARD"></interp>EDWARD HOLT</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Great Bland-street, Dover-road; on the 23rd of Jan. I was passing from Duke-street to Lincoln's Inn-fields—I heard a noise, looked back, and found a gentleman with the prisoner in his arms—I went on, and found my handkerchief was gone—this is it.</p>
               <p>
