                        <interp inst="t18430130-name-933" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES DILLON</persName>
                  </hi>. I was going through Lincoln's Inn-fields with Holt—I heard a cry, and saw a gentleman holding the prisoner—I went on, then I looked round again, and saw the officer had got the prisoner—I saw the handkerchief taken from his trowsers' pocket.</p>
